<h2>BCC1997: Calculation of Option Prices Based on a Universal Solution</h2>
<p>Calculates the prices of European options based on the universal solution provided by Bakshi, Cao and Chen (1997) &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1540-6261.1997.tb02749.x">doi:10.1111/j.1540-6261.1997.tb02749.x</a>&gt;. This solution considers stochastic volatility, stochastic interest and random jumps. Please cite their work if this package is used. </p>
